- The achievement check was already wired in `useGameLoop.ts` via `discoveryCount` (counts `speciesProgress[*].tier >= 1`), so `seenInWild=true → tier=1` automatically feeds the existing "Keen Eye" and "Codex Scholar" achievement checks with zero extra wiring
